text: Kurtlyn Mannikam (born 19 January 1996) is a South African first-class cricketer. He was included in the KZN Inland squad for the 2016 Africa T20 Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:KwaZulu-Natal Inland cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
